<div class='jumbotron bg-secondary text-white mt-3'>
  <h1 class='display-3 text-center'>Generate Reports</h1>
</div>
<div class="row mb-3">
  <div class="col-md-2">
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div class="card bg-secondary text-white">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>On this page, you can generate real-time reports on select data.</p>
        <p>To create the report, simply click on a link below.</p>
        <p>Each report has a button at the bottom that will allow you to create a PDF of the report and print as necessary.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-2">
  </div>
</div>
